#compdef texlab
# Documentation: https://github.com/latex-lsp/texlab
# Reference accessed: 2026-05-21
# Verified: upstream repo at the URL above. README does not document
# CLI flags; standard LSP server runs without args. The following flags
# are intentionally left minimal — additional flags should be verified
# via `texlab --help` against the actual installed binary.

_arguments -s -S \
  '(- *)'{-h,--help}'[show help]' \
  '(- *)'{-V,--version}'[show version]'
